text: Krasny Kushak () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Ivano-Kuvalatsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Zilair, 18 km from Ivano-Kuvalat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Krasny Kushak
